rComments: Quite possibly my favourite professor of all time. An entertaining and super friendly person. Work hard, participate, and he will show he cares about you. Would highly recommend his courses!

So listen, I had this professor at Humber College North. He is by far the best thing that's ever happened to my English skills. He's always there for you and is very reasonable when it comes to assignments. He's always cracking jokes and keeping the class interesting. Would take again and again.
Great class, great prof, not hard to do well if you pay attention and know how to write an essay! Very friendly + approachable + understanding
Awesome prof. Very clear. Makes things interesting.
Very helpful and insightful. He provides in depth comments on essays and is extremely accessible and approachable.
